Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Place an explosive barrel that will explode when hit or after 10 seconds

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Use your jump boots to launch high into the air.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Wreath your weapon in pure electricity and slash it in a wide arc in front of you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Rise into the air and unleash several extremely powerful magical projectiles.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Rapidly slash your sword in front of you, dealing substantial damage to anything in your way.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Slice in rapic succession while moving forward.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon an aura that will slow any enemy that steps on it.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast an ice enchantment ring. Any arrows shot through the ring will be enchanted with ice.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Slowly freezes any enemy that it touches for a short amount of time.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a ball of pure force. Send weak enemies flying.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Disperse into a mist and relocate to a nearby location extremely quickly. Useful when cornered.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A devastating uppercut that can send enemies flying.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Increases the size of the nearest physics object.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Toss a big bomb that deals moderate damage, but pushes enemies away from the explosion area.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Stomp your foot into the ground, launching a medium-size boulder out of the ground and into the air directly in front of you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A larger version of Arcane Bolt. More magic, more damage, longer cooldown.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A larger version of Arcane Bolt. More magic, more damage, longer cooldown.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Heal youself 50 points.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Heal youself 50 points.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a small rock from the ground. Can be picked up and used as a weapon or thrown.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a small rock from the ground. Can be picked up and used as a weapon or thrown.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call down a massive meteor from the skies to annihilate your enemies. Will arch through the sky to impact at the area you point at when casting the spell.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call down a massive meteor from the skies to annihilate your enemies. Will arch through the sky to impact at the area you point at when casting the spell.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast a ball of molten metal that allows for mortar-like attacks!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a ball of molten metal that allows for mortar-like attacks!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Pushes the object you are looking at with great force. Must be looking at physics-based object to have effect.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Pushes the object you are looking at with great force. Must be looking at physics-based object to have effect.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Pulls the object you are looking at towards you. Must be looking at physics-based object to have effect.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Pulls the object you are looking at towards you. Must be looking at physics-based object to have effect.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summons a bolt of lightning from the sky
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summons a bolt of lightning from the sky

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: HOLD and RELEASE to summon several bolts of lightning from the sky
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: HOLD and RELEASE to summon several bolts of lightning from the sky

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a beam of pure electricity from your hands. Can enchant physics objects with electricity for 15 seconds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a beam of pure electricity from your hands. Can enchant physics objects with electricity for 15 seconds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire an extremely fast bolt of electricity that explodes with great force. Can enchant objects with electricity
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire an extremely fast bolt of electricity that explodes with great force. Can enchant objects with electricity

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A concentrated beam of molten lead. Ignites enemies and objects.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A concentrated beam of molten lead. Ignites enemies and objects.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Jump into the air and quickly stab diagonally downwards, dealing damage and making enemies bleed
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Jump into the air and quickly stab diagonally downwards, dealing damage and making enemies bleed

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swing your weapon extremely fast and finish with an aerial strike, wreathed in flame
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swing your weapon extremely fast and finish with an aerial strike, wreathed in flame

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw any physics object into the Rune Ring and it will ingite with magical fire.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw any physics object into the Rune Ring and it will ingite with magical fire.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A bolt of ice that freezes anything it touches
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A bolt of ice that freezes anything it touches

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A concentrated beam of frost that freezes all in its path
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A concentrated beam of frost that freezes all in its path

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw any physics object into the Rune Ring and it will freeze in place. Useful when objects are being thrown at you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw any physics object into the Rune Ring and it will freeze in place. Useful when objects are being thrown at you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Conjure a huge wall of ice that lasts for 15 seconds before melting.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Conjure a huge wall of ice that lasts for 15 seconds before melting.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge your weapon for a devastating stab which blasts a beam of energy out of the tip of your weapon.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge your weapon for a devastating stab which blasts a beam of energy out of the tip of your weapon.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Stomp the ground, launching nearby objects into the air then preform a spinning attack that launches objects in front of you with great force
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Stomp the ground, launching nearby objects into the air then preform a spinning attack that launches objects in front of you with great force

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swing your shield in front of you. Doesn't deal a whole lot of damage, but makes weak enemies ragdoll and tough enemies stagger.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swing your shield in front of you. Doesn't deal a whole lot of damage, but makes weak enemies ragdoll and tough enemies stagger.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw your shield with great force before calling it back to your hand.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw your shield with great force before calling it back to your hand.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge your weapon with electrical magic then jump forward, cutting in front of you and calling a bolt of lightning to strike in front of you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge your weapon with electrical magic then jump forward, cutting in front of you and calling a bolt of lightning to strike in front of you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Leap forward and slice downward, causing a great deal of damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Leap forward and slice downward, causing a great deal of damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Slam the ground, staggering enemies with a slight chance of ragdolling them. Afer the third strike, unleash an earth-based attack, ravaging enemies in your path.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Slam the ground, staggering enemies with a slight chance of ragdolling them. Afer the third strike, unleash an earth-based attack, ravaging enemies in your path.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire this arrow into the air. After a short moment, it will automatically shoot toward the nearest enemy.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire this arrow into the air. After a short moment, it will automatically shoot toward the nearest enemy.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire three arrows at once in a cone in front of you. Each arrow does 70 damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire three arrows at once in a cone in front of you. Each arrow does 70 damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire an arrow that has a chance to freeze enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire an arrow that has a chance to freeze enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An incredibly powerful strike that decapitates enemies if it deals the killing blow.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An incredibly powerful strike that decapitates enemies if it deals the killing blow.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A heavy two handed strike. Deals substantial damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A heavy two handed strike. Deals substantial damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A quick low sweep that can hit many enemies at once.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A quick low sweep that can hit many enemies at once.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A powerful downward slash that, upon impact, releases a small explosion.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A powerful downward slash that, upon impact, releases a small explosion.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Loose 3 arrows into the air that burst into smaller arrows that rain down upon your enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Loose 3 arrows into the air that burst into smaller arrows that rain down upon your enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a boar that charges at the marker that is placed on the ground when casting the spell.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a boar that charges at the marker that is placed on the ground when casting the spell.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cause an eruption of fire to spew from the ground where ever you might be looking.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cause an eruption of fire to spew from the ground where ever you might be looking.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a spinning hammer made of pure mana. Enemies hit by the hammer take 75 damage and are sent flying.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a spinning hammer made of pure mana. Enemies hit by the hammer take 75 damage and are sent flying.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast an orb of dark magic that explodes the target from the inside. If the enemy is killed by the explosion, all of their limbs are dismembered in the explosion.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast an orb of dark magic that explodes the target from the inside. If the enemy is killed by the explosion, all of their limbs are dismembered in the explosion.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cause an eruption of fire to spew from the ground where ever you might be looking.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cause an eruption of fire to spew from the ground where ever you might be looking.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Slow time then unleash a series of strikes.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Slow time then unleash a series of strikes.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Make all nearby enemies fly into the air before being propelled back to the ground at high speeds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Make all nearby enemies fly into the air before being propelled back to the ground at high speeds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Make all light to mid-weight enemies float into the air for a few seconds before dropping back to the ground.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Make all light to mid-weight enemies float into the air for a few seconds before dropping back to the ground.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a large bubble that slows down projectiles and enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a large bubble that slows down projectiles and enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Freeze all enemies around you for 10 seconds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Freeze all enemies around you for 10 seconds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon the Spear of Iher to impale an enemy.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon the Spear of Iher to impale an enemy.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Motivate your troops with a battlecry! Increases friendly troop attack and movement speed
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Motivate your troops with a battlecry! Increases friendly troop attack and movement speed

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Orders all shield-bearing troops to form a line and raise their shields. Doubles their defence.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Orders all shield-bearing troops to form a line and raise their shields. Doubles their defence.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: All nearby troops abandon their current task and follow you. Useful when getting out of tight spots!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: All nearby troops abandon their current task and follow you. Useful when getting out of tight spots!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Orders all of your bow or crossbow-wielding troops to release two volleys of arrows.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Orders all of your bow or crossbow-wielding troops to release two volleys of arrows.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Orders all of your musket-wielding troops to fire at the designated location.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Orders all of your musket-wielding troops to fire at the designated location.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Imbue your weapon with Manafire. Your weapon will now ignite enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Imbue your weapon with Manafire. Your weapon will now ignite enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Imbue your weapon with Manafrost. You weapon now chills the enemy, slowing their movement.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Imbue your weapon with Manafrost. You weapon now chills the enemy, slowing their movement.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Imbue your weapon with Manathunder. Your weapon deals more damage and has a chance to blast enemies away upon killing them.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Imbue your weapon with Manathunder. Your weapon deals more damage and has a chance to blast enemies away upon killing them.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast six slowing projectiles then finish with a powerful leaping strike!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast six slowing projectiles then finish with a powerful leaping strike!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Double your unarmed damage and unleash a flurry of extremely rapid blows.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Double your unarmed damage and unleash a flurry of extremely rapid blows.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Stomp the ground, summoning a block of stone in front of you. SHOVE the block to send it sliding forwards!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Stomp the ground, summoning a block of stone in front of you. SHOVE the block to send it sliding forwards!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Use when unarmed. Turn your fists to stone. While spell is active, unarmed attacks deal 3x damage!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Use when unarmed. Turn your fists to stone. While spell is active, unarmed attacks deal 3x damage!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Kick while dragging your foot on the ground, creating a ball of earthen energy that quickly blasts off your foot!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Kick while dragging your foot on the ground, creating a ball of earthen energy that quickly blasts off your foot!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A soothing tune that heals you!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A soothing tune that heals you!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summons a small orb of light that follows you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summons a small orb of light that follows you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A tune that ignites the ground around you!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A tune that ignites the ground around you!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A dark tune that summons a cloud of poisonous gas.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A dark tune that summons a cloud of poisonous gas.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A fierce melody that casts a ball of fire!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A fierce melody that casts a ball of fire!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A beautiful tune that makes all nearby enemies and objects weightless!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A beautiful tune that makes all nearby enemies and objects weightless!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A haunting song that changes the weather!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A haunting song that changes the weather!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A light song that summons a cloud that can be grappled and walked on.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A light song that summons a cloud that can be grappled and walked on.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast a ball of disease that poisons enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a ball of disease that poisons enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Automatically target 3 enemies, teleport to them and slash them with your weapon multiple times!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Automatically target 3 enemies, teleport to them and slash them with your weapon multiple times!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot an arrow that allows you to see through the arrows perspective and control it with your mind!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot an arrow that allows you to see through the arrows perspective and control it with your mind!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Pick up and throw your target!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Pick up and throw your target!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw an enchanted flaming hammer that detonates after a short period.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw an enchanted flaming hammer that detonates after a short period.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A sphere of frost magic. Enemies that reside in the sphere for too long are frozen solid.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A sphere of frost magic. Enemies that reside in the sphere for too long are frozen solid.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Warp forwad and slash your weapon, dealing 3x the weapons damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Warp forwad and slash your weapon, dealing 3x the weapons damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Lift into the air before casting 3 bolts of bolts of pure natural energy.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Lift into the air before casting 3 bolts of bolts of pure natural energy.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a deadly spike wall, just waiting for you to kick an enemy into it.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a deadly spike wall, just waiting for you to kick an enemy into it.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a ravenous flock of carrion birds from your palm that attach to enemies and deal sigificant damage over time.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a ravenous flock of carrion birds from your palm that attach to enemies and deal sigificant damage over time.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a great skeletal hand from the depths of hell to launch your enemies through the air.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a great skeletal hand from the depths of hell to launch your enemies through the air.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into a Direwolf for 30 seconds. Pressing E at any time will transform you back to your human form.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into a Direwolf for 30 seconds. Pressing E at any time will transform you back to your human form.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into the physical form of Taro, the mighty flamed hawk.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into the physical form of Taro, the mighty flamed hawk.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into a Reaping, plaguing those in your path.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into a Reaping, plaguing those in your path.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a sentient metallic skull with great force. Upon impact, the skull lets out a scream and launches in a random direction.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a sentient metallic skull with great force. Upon impact, the skull lets out a scream and launches in a random direction.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into a Rimebeak, a large, ice-element bird.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into a Rimebeak, a large, ice-element bird.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into the lightning-wreathed bird, the Thunderbill.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into the lightning-wreathed bird, the Thunderbill.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into a bird that explodes upon impact!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into a bird that explodes upon impact!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Take the form of a fire dragon.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Take the form of a fire dragon.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A deadly double kick. The first kick launches the target into the air, the second kick impacts the enemy with great force and ignites them.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A deadly double kick. The first kick launches the target into the air, the second kick impacts the enemy with great force and ignites them.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon the Bow of the Ancients, a shortbow that shoots extremely fast, explosive arrows. Lasts 15 seconds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon the Bow of the Ancients, a shortbow that shoots extremely fast, explosive arrows. Lasts 15 seconds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Warp behind your targeted enemy perform a series of devastating stab attacks. The first hit does x3 damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Warp behind your targeted enemy perform a series of devastating stab attacks. The first hit does x3 damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Lift into the air before casting 3 bolts of bolts of pure natural energy.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Lift into the air before casting 3 bolts of bolts of pure natural energy.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into a random piece of furniture! Jumping when in this form launches the object in the direction you are looking.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into a random piece of furniture! Jumping when in this form launches the object in the direction you are looking.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot a balloon attached to an arrow. Lifts physics objects and enemies, provided you attach enough balloons.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot a balloon attached to an arrow. Lifts physics objects and enemies, provided you attach enough balloons.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a massive anvil that, if it hits the ground hard enough, launches nearby enemies into the air.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a massive anvil that, if it hits the ground hard enough, launches nearby enemies into the air.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Any arrows/bullets shot through the ring are transformed into bolts of thunder.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Any arrows/bullets shot through the ring are transformed into bolts of thunder.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot a massive wooden spike that attaches to nearly any surface, allowing you to attach you grapple hook to it.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot a massive wooden spike that attaches to nearly any surface, allowing you to attach you grapple hook to it.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a handful of angry pitchfork-wielding peasants. Also summons a pitchfor for you so that you can join in on the angry mob.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a handful of angry pitchfork-wielding peasants. Also summons a pitchfor for you so that you can join in on the angry mob.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Curse the targeted ground with undead magic. Undead hands grab at the ankles of any passerby!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Curse the targeted ground with undead magic. Undead hands grab at the ankles of any passerby!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into a massive but slow ent!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into a massive but slow ent!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Toss your shield under your feet and surf!! Careful, hitting objects or falling too far will cause you to ragdoll!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Toss your shield under your feet and surf!! Careful, hitting objects or falling too far will cause you to ragdoll!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a giant, super bouncy mushroom!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a giant, super bouncy mushroom!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast 3 bolts of nature bolts that spread through the ground and sprout several explosive shrooms each. Natural minefields!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast 3 bolts of nature bolts that spread through the ground and sprout several explosive shrooms each. Natural minefields!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Encase your target in a stone prison, weakening them. Any damage done to the enemy while imprisoned is doubled.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Encase your target in a stone prison, weakening them. Any damage done to the enemy while imprisoned is doubled.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Turn into a chicken! Pressing E will cause the chicken to explode.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Turn into a chicken! Pressing E will cause the chicken to explode.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw an elemental chain that immobilzes your target. Hitting the chain with an elemental spell will cause the chain to absorb the element and magnify its damage!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw an elemental chain that immobilzes your target. Hitting the chain with an elemental spell will cause the chain to absorb the element and magnify its damage!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Turn any physics-based object into a mount!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Turn any physics-based object into a mount!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a small volcano that waits for enemies to get close before erupting!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a small volcano that waits for enemies to get close before erupting!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Marks an enemy to duel in the Spectral Arena. All damage input, output, mana consumption and all rewards are doubled.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Marks an enemy to duel in the Spectral Arena. All damage input, output, mana consumption and all rewards are doubled.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a pillar of rock that can be used to reach high places or to get out of a sticky situation.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a pillar of rock that can be used to reach high places or to get out of a sticky situation.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Turn any physics-based object into a spider mount for 30 seconds!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Turn any physics-based object into a spider mount for 30 seconds!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Give any physics object wings and make it into a mount! Press space while mounted to flap wings!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Give any physics object wings and make it into a mount! Press space while mounted to flap wings!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon an Ichorian Blade - A powerful sword that only lasts for 35 seconds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon an Ichorian Blade - A powerful sword that only lasts for 35 seconds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast this spell on any enemy corpse to reanimate it. The body will wander and attack any enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast this spell on any enemy corpse to reanimate it. The body will wander and attack any enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon 3 Spectral Warriors for a short time.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon 3 Spectral Warriors for a short time.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Deploy a spider bomb that walks forwards and detonates when near and enemy or when hit by a projectile.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Deploy a spider bomb that walks forwards and detonates when near and enemy or when hit by a projectile.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast this spell upon a corpse. After a short delay, the corpse bursts, creating a deadly, bloodly explosion.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast this spell upon a corpse. After a short delay, the corpse bursts, creating a deadly, bloodly explosion.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summons a barrage of barrels.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summons a barrage of barrels.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon two portals!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon two portals!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Paralyze an enemy - every hit to the enemy will increase the force applied to them when the paralysis expires.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Paralyze an enemy - every hit to the enemy will increase the force applied to them when the paralysis expires.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a Blood Golem. Grows with every kill!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a Blood Golem. Grows with every kill!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Toss a Spiritstone that will absorb a stunned animal!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Toss a Spiritstone that will absorb a stunned animal!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Warp in the direction you are looking. 2 charges before triggering cooldown.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Warp in the direction you are looking. 2 charges before triggering cooldown.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw magical daggers that stick into any surface and detonate after a short delay. 3 charges before triggering cooldown.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw magical daggers that stick into any surface and detonate after a short delay. 3 charges before triggering cooldown.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw two spikes that stick to any surface. If close enough, the spikes will pull together.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw two spikes that stick to any surface. If close enough, the spikes will pull together.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Draw blood from yourself or another and shape it into a spear, which is then thrown.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Draw blood from yourself or another and shape it into a spear, which is then thrown.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Initial cast marks physics object or enemy. Second cast swaps your position with the marked target!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Initial cast marks physics object or enemy. Second cast swaps your position with the marked target!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot two arrows that link together via a magical chain.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot two arrows that link together via a magical chain.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Play your lute and attract nearby people. As you play, the people watching slowly donate gold to you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Play your lute and attract nearby people. As you play, the people watching slowly donate gold to you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Allows you to glide while firing 3 bolts of ice!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Allows you to glide while firing 3 bolts of ice!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot a small shard of ice from your fingertip.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot a small shard of ice from your fingertip.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot a long, sharp spear of ice that impales enemies before shattering!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot a long, sharp spear of ice that impales enemies before shattering!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast a beam of frost magic that freezes any surface it touches, turning it into frozen ground, which enemies can slip on!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a beam of frost magic that freezes any surface it touches, turning it into frozen ground, which enemies can slip on!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast a beam of ice that creates large icicles that, after a short time, shoot off of the surface they're attached to.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a beam of ice that creates large icicles that, after a short time, shoot off of the surface they're attached to.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast a beam of concentrated frost magic that, upon impact with a surface, instantly freezes into a block of ice that you can walk on.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a beam of concentrated frost magic that, upon impact with a surface, instantly freezes into a block of ice that you can walk on.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A beam of magma that ingites any surface it hits!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A beam of magma that ingites any surface it hits!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Blast a wave of flames from your palm. Short range, but ignites anything the flames touch.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Blast a wave of flames from your palm. Short range, but ignites anything the flames touch.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a jet of steam that deals no damage, but can be used to launch enemies, objects or even yourself!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a jet of steam that deals no damage, but can be used to launch enemies, objects or even yourself!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: First cast summons a moving thundercloud. Second cast stops the cloud in its position and strike the ground beneath it!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: First cast summons a moving thundercloud. Second cast stops the cloud in its position and strike the ground beneath it!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Warp forward with your very being imbued with manathunder. If you warp towards the ground from a height, you will cause a thunderous explosion around you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Warp forward with your very being imbued with manathunder. If you warp towards the ground from a height, you will cause a thunderous explosion around you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Paralyze your enemies, making it difficult for them to land hits.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Paralyze your enemies, making it difficult for them to land hits.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Chuck a fist-sized rock.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Chuck a fist-sized rock.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw an axe!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw an axe!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A simple spell that can provide light when needed.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A simple spell that can provide light when needed.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Turn into a Goblin Whelp. Tricks enemies, so they will not attack you (unless you attack them)
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Turn into a Goblin Whelp. Tricks enemies, so they will not attack you (unless you attack them)

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Stomp the ground, calling forth a circle of stone to protect you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Stomp the ground, calling forth a circle of stone to protect you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot a magical arrow that provides a great source of light!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot a magical arrow that provides a great source of light!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot an arrow of frost, freezing all in its path.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot an arrow of frost, freezing all in its path.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot an arrow that morphs into a cannonball after a short time!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot an arrow that morphs into a cannonball after a short time!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot two arrows to create a tripwire that causes enemies to ragdoll!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot two arrows to create a tripwire that causes enemies to ragdoll!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Turn the target into stone for a brief period.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Turn the target into stone for a brief period.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Wreath yourself in magical bats that carry you forwards!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Wreath yourself in magical bats that carry you forwards!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Makes any physics object inflate and explode! Detonation happens after 2 seconds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Makes any physics object inflate and explode! Detonation happens after 2 seconds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw your weapon then pull yourself to its location!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw your weapon then pull yourself to its location!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Feed on the blood of your victim. Your vampiric blood makes the victim black out during the bite and immediately seals the bite wound when your teeth are removed.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Feed on the blood of your victim. Your vampiric blood makes the victim black out during the bite and immediately seals the bite wound when your teeth are removed.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Gonjure a tornado that can throw objects and enemies, or even provide you with some lift!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Gonjure a tornado that can throw objects and enemies, or even provide you with some lift!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Take the form of a magical mist for 5 seconds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Take the form of a magical mist for 5 seconds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fear the sun no more. Cast into the air to give yourself shade.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fear the sun no more. Cast into the air to give yourself shade.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Become a one with the shadows, literally. Melt into the ground and gain increased movment speed and invisibility. If you leave the shadows, you'll be forced to reveal yourself.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Become a one with the shadows, literally. Melt into the ground and gain increased movment speed and invisibility. If you leave the shadows, you'll be forced to reveal yourself.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Initial cast marks area for extraction - follow up casts pulls rocks from the marked location and launches them at your target.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Initial cast marks area for extraction - follow up casts pulls rocks from the marked location and launches them at your target.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Enhance your vision for the night or any dark area.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Enhance your vision for the night or any dark area.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An arrow wreathed in bees!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An arrow wreathed in bees!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a shield of mana, stopping any projectile in its tracks.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a shield of mana, stopping any projectile in its tracks.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon winds from your hand, allowing you to push objects and enemies and also provides some lift to you!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon winds from your hand, allowing you to push objects and enemies and also provides some lift to you!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Attaches a geyser of flame onto any surface!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Attaches a geyser of flame onto any surface!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast a concentrated jet of flame from your palm, allowing you to fly for a very short duration.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a concentrated jet of flame from your palm, allowing you to fly for a very short duration.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a spike of magma that, after a few seconds, detonates, spraying magma in a cone.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a spike of magma that, after a few seconds, detonates, spraying magma in a cone.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot a small projectile of manafire that deals little damage but can be fired in quick succession.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot a small projectile of manafire that deals little damage but can be fired in quick succession.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call down a small meteor from the sun. Takes a short time to hit the target, but the results are deadly.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call down a small meteor from the sun. Takes a short time to hit the target, but the results are deadly.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Stomp the ground, calling forth a burst of flame at the targeted location.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Stomp the ground, calling forth a burst of flame at the targeted location.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a ball of concentrated manafire that sticks to any surface before detonating.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a ball of concentrated manafire that sticks to any surface before detonating.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast on a corpse. Lifts the body from the ground and makes the flesh burst from their bones.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast on a corpse. Lifts the body from the ground and makes the flesh burst from their bones.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A short-range spell that mimics deadly claws - can even tear bones from flesh!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A short-range spell that mimics deadly claws - can even tear bones from flesh!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a deathly hand that launches forward, damaging and slowing enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a deathly hand that launches forward, damaging and slowing enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Rip a fragment of your targets soul from thier body, turning it against them.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Rip a fragment of your targets soul from thier body, turning it against them.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: If killed by the spell (or if spell is casted on a corpse), the targets head will rip off of its body and become your companion for a short time. Holding RMB and Left Clicking will launch the skull!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: If killed by the spell (or if spell is casted on a corpse), the targets head will rip off of its body and become your companion for a short time. Holding RMB and Left Clicking will launch the skull!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Let out a ghostly scream, making nearby enemies flee in fear.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Let out a ghostly scream, making nearby enemies flee in fear.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a Watchers Portal that spawns 10 small Watchers that seek targets and explode!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a Watchers Portal that spawns 10 small Watchers that seek targets and explode!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a Watcher from your palm that seeks the nearest enemy.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a Watcher from your palm that seeks the nearest enemy.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Possess any physics object with a Watcher. Any enemies nearby will be targeted by the Watcher, launching homing projectiles at them.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Possess any physics object with a Watcher. Any enemies nearby will be targeted by the Watcher, launching homing projectiles at them.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a barrage of exploding bones that launch in an arch.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a barrage of exploding bones that launch in an arch.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast on any physics object to make it yell out insults to attract NPC's!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast on any physics object to make it yell out insults to attract NPC's!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a spear of bone that can impale enemies. After a short delay, the spear explodes, sending splinters in all directions
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a spear of bone that can impale enemies. After a short delay, the spear explodes, sending splinters in all directions

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon and throw an enchanted skull that detonates after 2 seconds!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon and throw an enchanted skull that detonates after 2 seconds!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Glide forward, leaving a trail of flame behind you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Glide forward, leaving a trail of flame behind you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast an extremely fast bolt of dark magic. If there is a target close enough, the bolt will attempt to seek the closest target.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast an extremely fast bolt of dark magic. If there is a target close enough, the bolt will attempt to seek the closest target.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call forth a cone of bone spikes from the ground!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call forth a cone of bone spikes from the ground!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a grenade of ice that explodes and freezes neaby enemies and objects
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a grenade of ice that explodes and freezes neaby enemies and objects

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon icicles to burst out of the ground in a line in front of you!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon icicles to burst out of the ground in a line in front of you!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Small shards of ice that deal little damage, but chill enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Small shards of ice that deal little damage, but chill enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon crystalized ice to burst from the ground, damaging and impaling enemies in its way.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon crystalized ice to burst from the ground, damaging and impaling enemies in its way.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Spin with your weapon extended, damaging enemies all around you. Deals x3 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Spin with your weapon extended, damaging enemies all around you. Deals x3 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A low slash that slows enemies, and if this attack deals the killing blow, chops legs off.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A low slash that slows enemies, and if this attack deals the killing blow, chops legs off.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: When in the air, activate this skill to plunge to the ground!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: When in the air, activate this skill to plunge to the ground!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Grab your target, immobilizing them. LMB to bash with your pommel and RMB to throw the enemy!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Grab your target, immobilizing them. LMB to bash with your pommel and RMB to throw the enemy!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Run your weapon through the belly of your enemy, dealing x6 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Run your weapon through the belly of your enemy, dealing x6 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge forward with your shield, dealing damage to any who stand in your way.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge forward with your shield, dealing damage to any who stand in your way.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Give yourself an extra mid-air boost!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Give yourself an extra mid-air boost!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Stab your weapon downwards into the enemy, dealing x3 weapon damage before ripping it out, dealing x3 damage again.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Stab your weapon downwards into the enemy, dealing x3 weapon damage before ripping it out, dealing x3 damage again.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Leap into the air and whip your weapon horizontally in front of you, creating a wall of flame.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Leap into the air and whip your weapon horizontally in front of you, creating a wall of flame.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: 4 deadly slashes that each deal x2 weapon damage. The final attack parries enemies that are under 50% health!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: 4 deadly slashes that each deal x2 weapon damage. The final attack parries enemies that are under 50% health!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Quickly dash forward while slashing your weapon. Deals x3 weapon damage. Can hit multiple enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Quickly dash forward while slashing your weapon. Deals x3 weapon damage. Can hit multiple enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A quick, deadly strike.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A quick, deadly strike.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Enter a stance with your weapon at the ready. Right before an enemy attacks, attack! Perfect hits deal x6 weapon damage. Missing the perfect attack deals x2 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Enter a stance with your weapon at the ready. Right before an enemy attacks, attack! Perfect hits deal x6 weapon damage. Missing the perfect attack deals x2 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Spin extremely fast with your weapon outward, consuming stamina for every second the skill is active.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Spin extremely fast with your weapon outward, consuming stamina for every second the skill is active.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Rip forwards, slashing your weapon. After a short delay, whomever was in your path takes damage. Deals x5 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Rip forwards, slashing your weapon. After a short delay, whomever was in your path takes damage. Deals x5 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Place a sticky bomb on any surface. Casting after placing bomb detonates it.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Place a sticky bomb on any surface. Casting after placing bomb detonates it.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Place a jumplift - a runestone that pushes objects upward!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Place a jumplift - a runestone that pushes objects upward!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw an Invesion
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw an Invesion

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A powerful frontal stab that deals x5 weapon damage!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A powerful frontal stab that deals x5 weapon damage!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Slash your spear in front of you, defying gravity as you slash. Each slash deals x3 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Slash your spear in front of you, defying gravity as you slash. Each slash deals x3 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A slash-stab combo! The first slash parries enemies. The second attack deals x3 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A slash-stab combo! The first slash parries enemies. The second attack deals x3 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Flash forward while slashing both of your daggers!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Flash forward while slashing both of your daggers!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Enhance your movement speed for 20 seconds!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Enhance your movement speed for 20 seconds!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An extremely rapid series of slashes and stabs!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An extremely rapid series of slashes and stabs!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Spin your spear above your head, creating enough lift to hover! Attack while hovering to perform a dive attack
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Spin your spear above your head, creating enough lift to hover! Attack while hovering to perform a dive attack

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw your dagger with a chain attached to it. Upon hitting an enemy or physics object, it will be pulled towards you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw your dagger with a chain attached to it. Upon hitting an enemy or physics object, it will be pulled towards you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Grab your target and repeatedly stab them in the stomach by mashing the left mouse button. Right click to throw enemy.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Grab your target and repeatedly stab them in the stomach by mashing the left mouse button. Right click to throw enemy.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw one of your daggers. If the dagger hits an enemy, you teleport to the enemy and stab them with your other dagger, dealing x10 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw one of your daggers. If the dagger hits an enemy, you teleport to the enemy and stab them with your other dagger, dealing x10 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Enchant your blood with pure rage. All melee damage is doubled, but with each beat of your heart, blood bursts from your mouth, damaging you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Enchant your blood with pure rage. All melee damage is doubled, but with each beat of your heart, blood bursts from your mouth, damaging you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Drain a small amount of blood from the target and use it to heal yourself.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Drain a small amount of blood from the target and use it to heal yourself.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Hold your hand in the air, absorbing the blood essence from all nearby enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Hold your hand in the air, absorbing the blood essence from all nearby enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: The targeted enemy is pulled into the air and their blood explodes from their pores, turning into bloodspikes and damaging all neaby foes.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: The targeted enemy is pulled into the air and their blood explodes from their pores, turning into bloodspikes and damaging all neaby foes.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Exchange your own blood for mana.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Exchange your own blood for mana.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Take control of a body, dead or alive. Press E while puppeting to detonate the controlled body's blood. While puppeting, your health is slowly drained.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Take control of a body, dead or alive. Press E while puppeting to detonate the controlled body's blood. While puppeting, your health is slowly drained.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Create a totem of blood that regenerates your mana if you are close enough.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Create a totem of blood that regenerates your mana if you are close enough.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Toss a smoke bomb, disappearing from sight for a short period!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Toss a smoke bomb, disappearing from sight for a short period!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Toss a shuriken that deals minor damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Toss a shuriken that deals minor damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge your shield with manathunder and throw it! If the shield hits an enemy, the electricity will arc to nearby enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge your shield with manathunder and throw it! If the shield hits an enemy, the electricity will arc to nearby enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Hold your shield over your head, allowing you to glide!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Hold your shield over your head, allowing you to glide!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a phantom version of your shield that plants itself into whatever surface it hits, making a platfrom for you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a phantom version of your shield that plants itself into whatever surface it hits, making a platfrom for you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast a spell that creates a dome in front of you the pushes away enemies and physics objects.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a spell that creates a dome in front of you the pushes away enemies and physics objects.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Plant your staff into the ground, having it act as a turret.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Plant your staff into the ground, having it act as a turret.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Create a large boulder that rolls forward, crushing enemies!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Create a large boulder that rolls forward, crushing enemies!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Produce a gentle beam of magic that charms and calms animals.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Produce a gentle beam of magic that charms and calms animals.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Raise your weapon above your head and ignite it with holy magic before slamming the magical energy down in front of you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Raise your weapon above your head and ignite it with holy magic before slamming the magical energy down in front of you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Change the weather! If it is raining, change it to clear skies and vice versa.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Change the weather! If it is raining, change it to clear skies and vice versa.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a flower that slowly grows into a mana-producing bulb that you can pick up!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a flower that slowly grows into a mana-producing bulb that you can pick up!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: The most basic form of Electromancy - a damaging spark. Has a low chance of electrifying enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: The most basic form of Electromancy - a damaging spark. Has a low chance of electrifying enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast a high-damage bolt that deals pure damage. Does not electrify enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast a high-damage bolt that deals pure damage. Does not electrify enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a Runecard with deadly power!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a Runecard with deadly power!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge a medium-sized fireball that detonates on impact!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge a medium-sized fireball that detonates on impact!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Twirl your spear in front of you, blocking attacks and reversing non-magic projectiles.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Twirl your spear in front of you, blocking attacks and reversing non-magic projectiles.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Hold your spear outward in front of you and dash forward!  Deals x5 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Hold your spear outward in front of you and dash forward!  Deals x5 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon holy blades to rain from the sky at the target area!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon holy blades to rain from the sky at the target area!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call forth a volley of holy arrows to rain down in an arch at the target location.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call forth a volley of holy arrows to rain down in an arch at the target location.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Blink toward the direction you are facing.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Blink toward the direction you are facing.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A short-range spell that summons a skeletal hand to claw at enemies!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A short-range spell that summons a skeletal hand to claw at enemies!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Drop down and slide, increasing move speed slightly. Can also trip enemies!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Drop down and slide, increasing move speed slightly. Can also trip enemies!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Take the form of a tiny, harmless beetle. Upon exiting the form, you are returned to the location that the spell was cast.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Take the form of a tiny, harmless beetle. Upon exiting the form, you are returned to the location that the spell was cast.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An advanced form of Warp Stab - this attack has longer range, locks onto targets and pulls you towards them before performing a deadly attack.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An advanced form of Warp Stab - this attack has longer range, locks onto targets and pulls you towards them before performing a deadly attack.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Sweep your weapon in a 360 degree slash!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Sweep your weapon in a 360 degree slash!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge with the butt of your weapon outward. Any unfortunate soul in your way will be taken for a ride before being thrown through the air!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge with the butt of your weapon outward. Any unfortunate soul in your way will be taken for a ride before being thrown through the air!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Slow time and defy gravity! Left click to throw kunai. After 3 are thrown, the skill ends.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Slow time and defy gravity! Left click to throw kunai. After 3 are thrown, the skill ends.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Lurch forward, slashing your weapon, dealing x5 weapon damage!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Lurch forward, slashing your weapon, dealing x5 weapon damage!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An exploding orb of blood that restores health based on the amount of damage dealt.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An exploding orb of blood that restores health based on the amount of damage dealt.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fill your weapon to the brim with blastpowder. Clicking at the right time unleshes a cone of flame that will blast enemies away!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fill your weapon to the brim with blastpowder. Clicking at the right time unleshes a cone of flame that will blast enemies away!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a bullet that ricochets off any surface! The more ricochets, the more power. Reach 5 bounces for insane damage!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a bullet that ricochets off any surface! The more ricochets, the more power. Reach 5 bounces for insane damage!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Reload your weapon in the blink of an eye!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Reload your weapon in the blink of an eye!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Affix a bayonet to your weapon and charge! Fire your weapon after impact for maximum effect.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Affix a bayonet to your weapon and charge! Fire your weapon after impact for maximum effect.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot a bullet covered in slime that coats the impact area! Enemies attempting to traverse the slime will be slowed significantly.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot a bullet covered in slime that coats the impact area! Enemies attempting to traverse the slime will be slowed significantly.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire an explosive bullet with a small blast radius. Also provides enough kick to boost your jumps!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire an explosive bullet with a small blast radius. Also provides enough kick to boost your jumps!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw flames from your weapons muzzle for 3 seconds!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw flames from your weapons muzzle for 3 seconds!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Enter a focused state, slowing your movement. Fire at the right time to deal significant damage and knock the enemy off their feet!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Enter a focused state, slowing your movement. Fire at the right time to deal significant damage and knock the enemy off their feet!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Freely fire your weapon without reloading for the duration of the skill!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Freely fire your weapon without reloading for the duration of the skill!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a bullet coated with poison. Deals minor impact damage, but significant damage over time.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a bullet coated with poison. Deals minor impact damage, but significant damage over time.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a bullet packed with poisonous gas. Upon impact, the bullet bursts, covering the area in poisonous gas!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a bullet packed with poisonous gas. Upon impact, the bullet bursts, covering the area in poisonous gas!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a barrel full of pellets for a shotgun-like blast!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a barrel full of pellets for a shotgun-like blast!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a dart that will put anything it hits to sleep.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a dart that will put anything it hits to sleep.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call forth deadly vines from the ground!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call forth deadly vines from the ground!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a large, unstable Bust Bulb. Detonates when it takes damage, or after 10 seconds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a large, unstable Bust Bulb. Detonates when it takes damage, or after 10 seconds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a magical arrow that detonates on impact. Fires in an arch, like a mortar.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a magical arrow that detonates on impact. Fires in an arch, like a mortar.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Launch yourself forward, weapon at the ready. Attacking while in the air will perform a mid-air strike, while landing on the ground will execute a radial damage attack.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Launch yourself forward, weapon at the ready. Attacking while in the air will perform a mid-air strike, while landing on the ground will execute a radial damage attack.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swing your weapon upward, making lightweight enemies that you strike fly into the air! Deals base weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swing your weapon upward, making lightweight enemies that you strike fly into the air! Deals base weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swing your weapon downwards, dealing 2.5x weapon damage. Cleaves or slams enemies, depending on equipped weapon type.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swing your weapon downwards, dealing 2.5x weapon damage. Cleaves or slams enemies, depending on equipped weapon type.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Hone your power, pouring it into your blade. For max damage, wait for the third charge! Click to perform the attack.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Hone your power, pouring it into your blade. For max damage, wait for the third charge! Click to perform the attack.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge forward with your weapon, unleashing a devistating stab attack that deals x5 weapon damage and pushes enemies away.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge forward with your weapon, unleashing a devistating stab attack that deals x5 weapon damage and pushes enemies away.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Unleash a flurry of attacks with your weapon! Each impact has a 10% chance to cause bleeding.
