Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Unleash a flurry of attacks with your weapon! Each impact has a 10% chance to cause bleeding.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call upon your ancestor's army to form a volley line behind you that rains down a massive amount of arrows!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call upon your ancestor's army to form a volley line behind you that rains down a massive amount of arrows!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call upon your ancestor's army to form a shield wall in front of you that rushes forward at your command.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call upon your ancestor's army to form a shield wall in front of you that rushes forward at your command.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An upward swing with a slight windup. Deals 2.5x weapon damage. Has a chance to ragdoll enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An upward swing with a slight windup. Deals 2.5x weapon damage. Has a chance to ragdoll enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A triple-stab attack that can cause bleeding!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A triple-stab attack that can cause bleeding!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A simple but powerful downward slash!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A simple but powerful downward slash!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Use your shield to smack enemies into the air!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Use your shield to smack enemies into the air!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge your weapon with energy, then fling that energy out in the form of several blades!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge your weapon with energy, then fling that energy out in the form of several blades!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Requires a blastspear. Focus the power of the blaststone and let loose a burst of flame from the tip of the blastspear!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Requires a blastspear. Focus the power of the blaststone and let loose a burst of flame from the tip of the blastspear!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swing your fist upwards with great force, launching yourself and the enemy you hit into the air!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swing your fist upwards with great force, launching yourself and the enemy you hit into the air!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Clasp your hands together and slam them downwards!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Clasp your hands together and slam them downwards!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A single, incredibly fast punch that creates a shockwave projectile that can ragdoll enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A single, incredibly fast punch that creates a shockwave projectile that can ragdoll enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swing your fists at immense speeds, striking enemies dozens of times before ending the attack with a powerful jab.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swing your fists at immense speeds, striking enemies dozens of times before ending the attack with a powerful jab.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Grab a ragdolled enemy by the ankels and spin them around, hitting enemies around you, then let them go!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Grab a ragdolled enemy by the ankels and spin them around, hitting enemies around you, then let them go!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Grab an enemy by their throat. Either mash LMB to repeatadly strike them, or click RMB to toss them.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Grab an enemy by their throat. Either mash LMB to repeatadly strike them, or click RMB to toss them.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Launch yourself forward with your leg outwards!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Launch yourself forward with your leg outwards!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Slam your weapon into the ground, splitting the earth and  making magma erupt from the cracks!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Slam your weapon into the ground, splitting the earth and  making magma erupt from the cracks!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Grow a pillar of ice at the targeted area! Hold to grow, release to end cast.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Grow a pillar of ice at the targeted area! Hold to grow, release to end cast.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An advanced form of Spear of Ice - Upon throwing, the spear bursts into small shards, allowing for multiple targets to be hit.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An advanced form of Spear of Ice - Upon throwing, the spear bursts into small shards, allowing for multiple targets to be hit.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw your weapon, making it spin rapidly before returning to your hand.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw your weapon, making it spin rapidly before returning to your hand.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Using Necrotic magic, you grab the targeted enemy by the throat and can throw or drop them.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Using Necrotic magic, you grab the targeted enemy by the throat and can throw or drop them.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Curse the ground underneath you, allowing you to absorb mana from any enemy who treads upon it.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Curse the ground underneath you, allowing you to absorb mana from any enemy who treads upon it.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon 15 mindless skeletons that do nothing but run at enemies and shatter. Will follow you if no enemies are nearby.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon 15 mindless skeletons that do nothing but run at enemies and shatter. Will follow you if no enemies are nearby.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swing your spear horizontally, knocking all enemies in front of you off their feet! Deals x3 weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swing your spear horizontally, knocking all enemies in front of you off their feet! Deals x3 weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon an orb of arcane light. Hitting the orb with any attack turns the incoming damage into projectiles that seek out nearby enemies!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon an orb of arcane light. Hitting the orb with any attack turns the incoming damage into projectiles that seek out nearby enemies!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Plunge your weapon into the ground, summoning massive Holy Blades to burst from the ground around you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Plunge your weapon into the ground, summoning massive Holy Blades to burst from the ground around you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A beam of soul energy that has a chance to absorb additional Spirit Essence from corpses.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A beam of soul energy that has a chance to absorb additional Spirit Essence from corpses.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a hammer of light that slams downward, crushing foes.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a hammer of light that slams downward, crushing foes.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a massive sword into your hands and perform a single, devistating slash!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a massive sword into your hands and perform a single, devistating slash!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: This skill is best used against ragdolled or already dead enemies. Plunge your weapon downwards in front of you - if the attack strikes a dead enemy, Divine Favor will be granted. Grants Arcane AND One Handed EXP.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: This skill is best used against ragdolled or already dead enemies. Plunge your weapon downwards in front of you - if the attack strikes a dead enemy, Divine Favor will be granted. Grants Arcane AND One Handed EXP.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Raise your shield in front of you, casting a cone of blinding light!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Raise your shield in front of you, casting a cone of blinding light!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An advanced form of the Final Rites prayer - blesses the ground around you.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An advanced form of the Final Rites prayer - blesses the ground around you.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: The most basic spell that every Arcane scholar knows. Can be used to bless corpses to put their souls to rest, granting you Divine Favor. Also provides minor healing.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: The most basic spell that every Arcane scholar knows. Can be used to bless corpses to put their souls to rest, granting you Divine Favor. Also provides minor healing.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon and throw a javelin made of arcane magic! Applies Divine Bond to targets until the javelin bursts.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon and throw a javelin made of arcane magic! Applies Divine Bond to targets until the javelin bursts.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Shoot a bolt of poison from your palm that deals minor damage upon impact and poisons enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Shoot a bolt of poison from your palm that deals minor damage upon impact and poisons enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swing your weapon horizontally in front of you, dealing x3 weapon damage. Has a chance to cause Bleed as well.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swing your weapon horizontally in front of you, dealing x3 weapon damage. Has a chance to cause Bleed as well.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Let out a ear-splitting battlecry that dizzies nearby enemies for 8 seconds!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Let out a ear-splitting battlecry that dizzies nearby enemies for 8 seconds!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Focus your energy into a powerful sweep attack that creates a cone of force in front of you!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Focus your energy into a powerful sweep attack that creates a cone of force in front of you!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Plunge your spear forwards, weakening targets.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Plunge your spear forwards, weakening targets.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Smack your spear downwards, nailing an enemy's head, making them dizzy!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Smack your spear downwards, nailing an enemy's head, making them dizzy!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Use your spear to leap forwards, leg extended!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Use your spear to leap forwards, leg extended!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A prayer taught to you by Esros himself. Used to destroy Warpstones.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A prayer taught to you by Esros himself. Used to destroy Warpstones.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Quickly rip your spear in and out of the target, causing them to bleed. Deals base weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Quickly rip your spear in and out of the target, causing them to bleed. Deals base weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: HOLD CAST to focus your inner energy into a unstable ball of pure mana. Release to unleash the energy!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: HOLD CAST to focus your inner energy into a unstable ball of pure mana. Release to unleash the energy!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a blessed arrow that, if it kills the targeted enemy, puts their soul to rest, granting you Divine Favor.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a blessed arrow that, if it kills the targeted enemy, puts their soul to rest, granting you Divine Favor.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire 3 magical bolts in quick succession!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire 3 magical bolts in quick succession!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire an arrow that, upon impact with an enemy, causes nearby enemies to flee in terror!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire an arrow that, upon impact with an enemy, causes nearby enemies to flee in terror!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a quick 3 round burst!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a quick 3 round burst!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Pull your bowstring until your bow is on the verge of snapping, then release!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Pull your bowstring until your bow is on the verge of snapping, then release!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Perform 4 stabs in quick succession that deal x2 weapon damage each!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Perform 4 stabs in quick succession that deal x2 weapon damage each!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An incredibly powerful punch that requires focus to reach its full potential.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An incredibly powerful punch that requires focus to reach its full potential.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Spread the gospel of Arosa! Chance to gain Divine Favor if your flyer hits a civilian. Also progresses Church of Arosa flyer objective, if active..
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Spread the gospel of Arosa! Chance to gain Divine Favor if your flyer hits a civilian. Also progresses Church of Arosa flyer objective, if active..

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A 3-hit ability that, when all 3 hits connect with an enemy, it makes them dizzy!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A 3-hit ability that, when all 3 hits connect with an enemy, it makes them dizzy!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Bless the targeted ground with Arcane Light - Any enemy that treads upon this ground takes minor Arcane damage and is debuffed with Divine Bond.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Bless the targeted ground with Arcane Light - Any enemy that treads upon this ground takes minor Arcane damage and is debuffed with Divine Bond.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A minor healing spell that restores a small amount of health.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A minor healing spell that restores a small amount of health.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: After a short charge up, cast a blast of electrical mana from your staff!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: After a short charge up, cast a blast of electrical mana from your staff!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Create a bubble shield that prevents enemies from getting too close. Can be upgraded to block projectiles as well.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Create a bubble shield that prevents enemies from getting too close. Can be upgraded to block projectiles as well.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Fire a volley of enemy-seeking Arcane projectiles!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Fire a volley of enemy-seeking Arcane projectiles!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Focus pyromantic energy at the edge of your staff before detonating it. Ignites enemies and surfaces in a cone in front of you!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Focus pyromantic energy at the edge of your staff before detonating it. Ignites enemies and surfaces in a cone in front of you!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An advanced form of an Arcane prayer that has a wide radius.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An advanced form of an Arcane prayer that has a wide radius.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Charge your staff with electrical magic, then blast it out in the form of a bolt!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Charge your staff with electrical magic, then blast it out in the form of a bolt!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Swipe your staff in front of you while summoning a cloud of poisonous gas!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Swipe your staff in front of you while summoning a cloud of poisonous gas!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a light upon your staff that acts as a torch. Hold RMB to increase the light's power.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a light upon your staff that acts as a torch. Hold RMB to increase the light's power.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A short range bolt of lightning that, upon hitting an enemy, arcs to other nearby enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A short range bolt of lightning that, upon hitting an enemy, arcs to other nearby enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: HOLD and RELEASE to summon a lightning bolt to strike at the desired location!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: HOLD and RELEASE to summon a lightning bolt to strike at the desired location!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: HOLD to cast a continuous flow of electrical energy that deals steady damage and has a chance to electrify enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: HOLD to cast a continuous flow of electrical energy that deals steady damage and has a chance to electrify enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Toss an electical rod that sticks into surfaces and arcs electircal damage to nearby enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Toss an electical rod that sticks into surfaces and arcs electircal damage to nearby enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Ignite your spear with manafire and perform a quick forward jab that ignites enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Ignite your spear with manafire and perform a quick forward jab that ignites enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Stomp your foot, calling forth a burst of earthly spikes from the ground.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Stomp your foot, calling forth a burst of earthly spikes from the ground.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a large rock that floats in the air. Pressing cast while the floating rock is spawned causes it to slam to the ground. Can be used as a platform as well as a trap! 15 mana to summon the rock, 15 mana to slam it down.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a large rock that floats in the air. Pressing cast while the floating rock is spawned causes it to slam to the ground. Can be used as a platform as well as a trap! 15 mana to summon the rock, 15 mana to slam it down.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon an orb of electricity that seeks out enemies who tread to close. High (80%) chance to electrify enemies!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon an orb of electricity that seeks out enemies who tread to close. High (80%) chance to electrify enemies!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Take the form of a Rabbit. With no attack, this form is best use as a means of movement.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Take the form of a Rabbit. With no attack, this form is best use as a means of movement.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call forth earthen energy that moves along the ground and seeks nearby enemies. Upon impacting with an enemy, it launches them into the air!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call forth earthen energy that moves along the ground and seeks nearby enemies. Upon impacting with an enemy, it launches them into the air!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Command the ground to encase the targets feet in stone, holding them in place!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Command the ground to encase the targets feet in stone, holding them in place!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a hammer for a single, devistating downward strike!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a hammer for a single, devistating downward strike!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: HOLD TO CAST. Encase yourself in stone and enter a meditative state that allows you to use the mana from the earth to heal yourself.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: HOLD TO CAST. Encase yourself in stone and enter a meditative state that allows you to use the mana from the earth to heal yourself.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Toss a spear of stone that can impale enemies!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Toss a spear of stone that can impale enemies!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a pair of stone slabs to raise from the ground and slam into one another. Enemies caught between them are sure to have a bad time.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a pair of stone slabs to raise from the ground and slam into one another. Enemies caught between them are sure to have a bad time.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a single, large firefly that floats around the area it was summoned, waiting to seek out and explode on a target!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a single, large firefly that floats around the area it was summoned, waiting to seek out and explode on a target!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a bird to fly at and peck the targeted enemy.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a bird to fly at and peck the targeted enemy.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into a boar and perform a single, deadly rush attack.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into a boar and perform a single, deadly rush attack.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a cursed rose that spits projectiles at nearby enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a cursed rose that spits projectiles at nearby enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a large bird that will attempt to lift the target enemy off the ground and hold them in the air.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a large bird that will attempt to lift the target enemy off the ground and hold them in the air.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Become an ethereal bear and perform a double-strike attack then return to your human form.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Become an ethereal bear and perform a double-strike attack then return to your human form.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Transform into a bear and let out a deafening roar that makes enemies flee in fear
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Transform into a bear and let out a deafening roar that makes enemies flee in fear

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Briefly take the form of a Raven, shooting upwards into the air!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Briefly take the form of a Raven, shooting upwards into the air!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Take the form of a ghostly sparrow. Short lifetime, so best used upon mid-range enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Take the form of a ghostly sparrow. Short lifetime, so best used upon mid-range enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a field of ivy to grow from the ground. Enemies who walk through the ivy are slowed significantly.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a field of ivy to grow from the ground. Enemies who walk through the ivy are slowed significantly.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Launch yourself into the air, taking the form of a small boulder!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Launch yourself into the air, taking the form of a small boulder!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Roll on the ground, morphing yourself into a rolling boulder.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Roll on the ground, morphing yourself into a rolling boulder.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A quick horizontal slash that aims for an enemy's throat! Deals x2 weapon damage and causes bleeding.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A quick horizontal slash that aims for an enemy's throat! Deals x2 weapon damage and causes bleeding.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Plunge your weapon forwards! Deals 3x damage to enemies. 6x if ragdolled, 12x if unconscious!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Plunge your weapon forwards! Deals 3x damage to enemies. 6x if ragdolled, 12x if unconscious!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Smack the enemy with the pommel of your weapon, making them dizzy for 3 seconds! Deals base weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Smack the enemy with the pommel of your weapon, making them dizzy for 3 seconds! Deals base weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A standard, fast, horizontal slash. Deals x6 weapon damage. Hitting surfaces creates SPARKS
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A standard, fast, horizontal slash. Deals x6 weapon damage. Hitting surfaces creates SPARKS

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A massively powerful strike that has a long wind-up. Deals x5 weapon damage!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A massively powerful strike that has a long wind-up. Deals x5 weapon damage!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A quick, somewhat weak slash that is mostly intended to be used to create SPARKS when striking a surface. Deals 1.5x weapon damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A quick, somewhat weak slash that is mostly intended to be used to create SPARKS when striking a surface. Deals 1.5x weapon damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Sit down and relax! Health regenerates twice as fast while kicking back.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Sit down and relax! Health regenerates twice as fast while kicking back.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Produce your pickaxe and perform a devistating downward smash. Instantly loots mining outcrops.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Produce your pickaxe and perform a devistating downward smash. Instantly loots mining outcrops.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Quickly summon a shield of ice in front of you. Blocks all projectiles, and can even launch enemies if cast underneath them!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Quickly summon a shield of ice in front of you. Blocks all projectiles, and can even launch enemies if cast underneath them!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a magical tree that increases magic, stamina and health regeneration.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a magical tree that increases magic, stamina and health regeneration.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a snowball! Deals 15 damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a snowball! Deals 15 damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Absorb spirit energy. While this spell does deal minor damage, its intended purpose is to absorb Lost Spirits, converting their energy into Necromancer EXP.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Absorb spirit energy. While this spell does deal minor damage, its intended purpose is to absorb Lost Spirits, converting their energy into Necromancer EXP.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw a boomerang-shaped shard of ice that returns to your hand after impact.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw a boomerang-shaped shard of ice that returns to your hand after impact.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: An crowd-pleasing skill, meant for use in an arena. Hype up the crowd, enticing them to throw you items.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: An crowd-pleasing skill, meant for use in an arena. Hype up the crowd, enticing them to throw you items.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Call down a small meteorite that explodes upon impact, causing the impact area to be covered in flames.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Call down a small meteorite that explodes upon impact, causing the impact area to be covered in flames.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: A hefty stomp. Best used on ragdolled enemies. x10 unarmed damage if done on an unconscious enemy.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: A hefty stomp. Best used on ragdolled enemies. x10 unarmed damage if done on an unconscious enemy.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Strike your enemy in the nose, causing them to become DIZZY. 25% chance to knock them unconscious.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Strike your enemy in the nose, causing them to become DIZZY. 25% chance to knock them unconscious.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Sweep your leg at your opponents feet, making them trip! Deals x3 Unarmed damage
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Sweep your leg at your opponents feet, making them trip! Deals x3 Unarmed damage

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Become a Werewolf. Form lasts for 10 minutes.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Become a Werewolf. Form lasts for 10 minutes.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a single, mindless skeleton that will run into the nearest enemy, shattering upon impact. Deals 50 damage.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a single, mindless skeleton that will run into the nearest enemy, shattering upon impact. Deals 50 damage.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Take the form of a unique, furless cat!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Take the form of a unique, furless cat!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Take the form of a basic raven for 30 seconds.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Take the form of a basic raven for 30 seconds.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Atune yourself to an object that is enchanted by nature itself. Druidic runestones, altars and maybe even some rock stacks can be activated with this spell.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Atune yourself to an object that is enchanted by nature itself. Druidic runestones, altars and maybe even some rock stacks can be activated with this spell.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a big, heavy tombstone above the target location! Upon impact, the tombstone shatters, dealing 150 damage to all enemies around it.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a big, heavy tombstone above the target location! Upon impact, the tombstone shatters, dealing 150 damage to all enemies around it.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Blare the Horn of Brittlebean, calling upon the Brittlbean Militia to assist you in combat!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Blare the Horn of Brittlebean, calling upon the Brittlbean Militia to assist you in combat!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Attune yourself to your lute and strum a single chord that creates a cone of force in the direction you are looking.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Attune yourself to your lute and strum a single chord that creates a cone of force in the direction you are looking.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a cloud underneath yourself that prevents fall damage and slowly descends.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a cloud underneath yourself that prevents fall damage and slowly descends.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Rain blood from the sky above you. Deals minor damage and weakens enemies.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Rain blood from the sky above you. Deals minor damage and weakens enemies.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a system of small planets that rotate around you for 30 seconds, damaging enemies they hit.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a system of small planets that rotate around you for 30 seconds, damaging enemies they hit.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Tranform into a bear! Form lasts for 1 minute.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Tranform into a bear! Form lasts for 1 minute.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Attach a small lantern to your hip that lights up a small area around you! Lasts 2 minutes.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Attach a small lantern to your hip that lights up a small area around you! Lasts 2 minutes.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Throw an explosive pumpkin-like grenade that deals 150 damage upon detonation!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Throw an explosive pumpkin-like grenade that deals 150 damage upon detonation!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a single Undead Walker to fight at your side!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a single Undead Walker to fight at your side!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a sword-wielding skeleton to fight with you!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a sword-wielding skeleton to fight with you!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a big, hammer-wielding skeleton to fight with you!
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a big, hammer-wielding skeleton to fight with you!

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Summon a scythe that spins around you for 8 seconds, cutting all in it's path! Deals 15 damage per hit.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Summon a scythe that spins around you for 8 seconds, cutting all in it's path! Deals 15 damage per hit.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Cast on an enemy with less than 20% health to warp to their location and explode them from within.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Cast on an enemy with less than 20% health to warp to their location and explode them from within.

Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.SourceString: Set up a zipline that launches a rope that allows you to traverse between the launch point and the impact point. Press JUMP at any time to jump off of the rope.
Description_9_DB349C0E417AC0D955ECD0AA95.LocalizedString: Set up a zipline that launches a rope that allows you to traverse between the launch point and the impact point. Press JUMP at any time to jump off of the rope.
